metadata.name: Ikuchi - [Water Yokai]
metadata.description:
🗦  イクチ  🗧

｡•★ Name - Ikuchi

｡•☆ Family - Water Yokai

｡•★ Habitat - Sea, Ocean

｡•☆ Origin - unknown

｡•★ Diet - it is unknown what she eats, but be careful

｡•☆ Description - Ikuchi are huge sea monsters that roam the open sea off the coast of Japan. In the Edo era, there were many stories where they were described as huge fish or some kind of sea snakes. Their bodies are covered with slippery oil that spreads around when they swim in the ocean.​‌‌​‌‌​ ​

The owner has the full right to use the design and illustration, excluding commercial use ~

//If you are the owner of Ikuchi, you can contact me and order her illustration~
